<h1>User Stories</h1>
<p>As a Customer side gateway the system should scan outgoing directory for *.mokesis files and for each file found, create one ISO20022 CustomerCreditTransferInitiationV03 message.</p>

<p>As a Customer side gateway the system should scan outgoing directory for *.taresis files and for each file found, create one ISO20022 CustomerCreditTransferInitiationV03 message.</p>

<p>As a Customer side gateway the system should be able to recieve ISO20022 BankToCustomerStatementV02  over Lithuanian Bank Association and VMI defined WSDL and create LITAS-ESIS statement file (*.acc) in the incoming directory.</p>

<p>
To be desided:
<ol>
 <li>How to convey payment status reports</li>
</ol>
</p>
